Class DHeap<K extends Comparable<K>, D>

java.lang.Object
datastructure.priorityqueue.DHeap<K,D>
Type Parameters:
K - type of the key value
D - type of the data object
All Implemented Interfaces:
PriorityQueue<K,D>
public class DHeap<K extends Comparable<K>, D> extends Object implements PriorityQueue<K,D>
Implementation using d-heap of a generic Priority Queue data structure composed of nodes of type DHeapNode containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
